    <a data-title="Importance" name="Importance"></a>
  


    <h2 class="expressive-heading-05  ">
        Why is AI-ready data important?
    </h2>
    








    

</div>
<div class="rich-text text"><div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-a373954bba" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Without trusted, high-quality and well-managed data, the outcomes of AI tools can be disappointing at best—and inaccurate, <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/ai-bias" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">biased</a> or a privacy risk at worst.</p>
<p>AI-ready data helps ensure that AI technologies deliver real business value and actionable insights by enabling:</p>

    
    
    
    

</div></div>
<div class="pictogram-item">
<c4d-content-item horizontal>
    
    
