    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    Stronger governance

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
        <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-bc28933d3d" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>AI-ready <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/dataset" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">datasets</a> arrive equipped with <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/data-privacy" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">data privacy</a> policies and data quality controls, which helps ensure that governance is embedded into processes and <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/data-pipeline" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">data pipelines</a> from day one.</p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
    </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    
</c4d-content-item>

    
    <script defer src="https://1.www.s81c.com/etc.clientlibs/adobe-cms/clientlibs/clientlib-content-item.lc-03de0bb71756db0bfcd670d4d5b12152-lc.min.js"></script>


</div>
