    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    Faster AI development

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
        <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-e409bd7999" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Established AI-ready data processes streamline the development of AI solutions by reducing time spent on accessing, understanding and preparing AI data.</p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
    </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    
</c4d-content-item>

    
    

</div>
<div class="pictogram-item">
<c4d-content-item horizontal>
    
    
