    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    Scalability for future projects

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
        <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-cb4316c6ab" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Correctly prepared and managed AI-ready data is an <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/interoperability" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">interoperable</a> and reusable asset that teams can leverage time and again for new and parallel AI projects.</p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
    </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    
</c4d-content-item>

    
    

</div>
