    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    Protection

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
        <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-a6ab5ebccc" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Robust protection measures safeguard data and help ensure its availability. These practices include firewalls, <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/encryption" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">encryption</a>, <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/endpoint-security" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">endpoint security</a>, <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/backup-and-restore" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">data backups</a>, <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/business-continuity" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">business continuity</a> and <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/disaster-recovery" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">disaster recovery</a> (<a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/business-continuity-disaster-recovery" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">BCDR</a>) plans, and services like <a href="https://www.ibm.com/think/topics/draas" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">disaster recovery as a service (DRaaS)</a>. <strong></strong></p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
    </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    
</c4d-content-item>

    
    

</div>
<div class="pictogram-item">
