    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    IBM® watsonx.data™

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-copy>
        <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
            <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-0226accc96" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Watsonx.data enables you to scale analytics and AI with all your data, wherever it resides, through an open, hybrid and governed data store.</p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
        </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    </c4d-content-item-copy>
    
    
    
        
        
        
        
        
        
